{"tid":1155643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"多圖 AKB女王 水著晒性感 超少布噴血寫真","createTime":"2019-05-15T05:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T14:33:45.000Z","uid":74065,"like":23,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1ded0925fcd70888828059afd8d6d08aa3ad34","tid":1155643,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=02c8bb55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=6bce250a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=83edde72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=b2f5e905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本女團SKE48的22歲一姐去年奪得《AKB48人氣總選》冠軍後，人氣更上一層樓。可惜今年停辦，加上AKB家族今年負面新聞不絕，突出的成員買少見少，令《AKB人氣總選》日後會否再舉行成疑，松井珠理奈大有機會成為末代一姐。而松井珠理奈獲第一名後，曾承諾會參加愛知縣名古屋市舉行的節慶巡遊，一年後終於兌現承諾，她日前出席巡遊，坐在開蓬跑車上同粉絲揮手，令在場約12,000人為之亢奮。另外，珠理奈又為漫畫雜誌拍水着寫真，難得大賣性感。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=33d08c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=eaeb402d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_08p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_08p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=09fe4be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190515/photo/bkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_09p.jpg?20190515130029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190515%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190515122132370-0515_00862_001_09p.jpg%3F20190515130029&h=88db2ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cba9974892b5e3e0675b3aba18d99d2c5f371d9","tid":1155643,"uid":171598,"like":85,"dislike":18,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"其實好撚柒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6Gn475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6Gn